Package: lollipop
Type: Package
Title: Detailed Lollipop Plots for Genomic Variants
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Jane", "Lane", email = "jlanej@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive R package for creating detailed lollipop plots to 
    visualize genomic variants with protein domains, Post-Translational 
    Modifications (PTMs), and variant annotations. Features include automatic 
    data retrieval from UniProt, variant visualization with VEP consequence 
    coloring, protein domain architecture display, and PTM visualization.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    dplyr,
    scales,
    ggrepel,
    httr,
    jsonlite
RoxygenNote: 7.0.0
URL: https://github.com/jlanej/lollipop
BugReports: https://github.com/jlanej/lollipop/issues
